d591885c0b03bc5f65879743e","tid":2351701,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"打丁無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526613d47c82596d6125c83be25e3d7db2960a86","tid":2351701,"uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"2020年11月19日，孔令寶因犯<span class=\"red\">受賄罪被判處有期徒刑10年6個月</span>，並處罰金人民幣60萬元，追繳<span class=\"red\">受賄所得上交國庫</span>。<br />\n<br />\n大陸做官個個都貪, 佢肯定係巨貪, 咁後生做領導加上串柒柒 個人飄,睇唔起祖國本世紀/史上偉大發明&quot;武肺病毒&quot; ，黨梗係收割你<br />\n有期徒刑, 屋企如果仲有錢淨嘅 坐一排再疏通下就出得返黎啦"},{"pid":"16f98d8cb7a8242367113cec2bba9cfa4af23721","tid":2351701,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"下個到林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea47069b1c23f79319ce587fc756cfd3d618238c","tid":2351701,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"照計好少事?<br />\n坐10碌似得罪人喎"},{"pid":"b840f43e33eda1ef61a6d97e10218b969c6da13b","tid":2351701,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:19:20.000Z","msg":"要做你真係打個飛機都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a238d60e04d188fb16da39c5bbc1ae7a958a013","tid":2351701,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"}]}